Attributes orient="N0" x=4440 y=8040
TextInfo text="Application Notes:\n1. The model will only run in SIMPLIS Versions 8.10a and above.\n2. The published testbench has been configured for 5VDC input, 5VDC  output\n3. The simulation uses ideal power FETS , Diodes , Tranformers, Inductors and Capacitors to speed up simulation time, simulation efficiency measurement will not match actual part\n4. All the decoupling capacitors at input and output do not include the bias voltage dependency to the capacitance reduction\n5. 0805 capacitor values are set based on the DC de-rating coeffecients at 5V operation for a 22uF nominal capacitor\n6. Thermal characteristics of the part have not been modeled.\n7. The 100K resitor added to the device output is required for simulation convergence only"
Property name="StyleNormal" value="LegacyFontFreeText" autopos=1 normal="Left" rotated="Left" visible=0 font="Default"
